	<h1 class="history-banner">Our History</h1>
	<div class="silver-bg">
		<p>The company was established in 1996 as an offshore development center for the parent company in Belgium, since then <span class="xsysys_style">xsysys</span> Technologies evolved into an autonomous state of the art IT-enabled facility in one of the most prominent IT- clusters in the world,“ Bangalore”, Silicon Valley of India”.</p>
		<p>The parent company DeDuCo is a leading Belgium-based, but globally expanding company with a rich history in developing and implementing Customer Relationship Management software solutions.</p>
		<p>After its foundation in 1987 DeDuCo grew into a major player with outstanding expertise in four selected market sectors: the Consumer Goods sector (Food and Nonfood), the Pharmaceutical OTC sector, the Hotel and Catering sector and the Vending machines sector.</p>
		<p>DeDuCo offers its customers company-wide software solutions and a wide range of related services. Its CRM software suite contains five integrated products (KEYaccount+, SALESforce+, SECtor+, CALLcenter+ and FIELDservice+), all of them ensuring the customers’ competitive edge. For more information, please visit <a href="http://www.deduco.com">www.deduco.com</a>.</p>
